name: Jindo Dog 진돗개
description: Jindo Dog ($JINDO) is a community-driven cryptocurrency built on the Ethereum blockchain. The project takes inspiration from the Jindo dog, a native Korean breed recognized for its loyalty, intelligence, and homing instinct. $JINDO aims to serve as a meme token that combines cultural heritage with blockchain participation, offering users a way to engage in decentralized communities while celebrating the symbolism of one of Korea’s most iconic dog breeds.
